ENTRY            40627   20260216   20260319   20260319       4226
SUBENT        40627001   20260216   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                 16         45
TITLE       Inelastic scattering of the neutrons with energies
            from 5 to 8 MeV on yttrium
AUTHOR     (S.P.Simakov,G.N.Lovchikova,V.P.Lunev,O.A.Sal'nikov,
           S.E.Sukhikh)
REFERENCE  (R,ZFK-491,206,1982)   Proceedings of the 12-th
            International Symposium on Nuclear Physics,Gaussig,GDR
            In Russian.
           ((J,YK,,(3-4),74,1992)=
           (R,INDC(CCP)-358,74,1992)) In English.
           (S,INDC(NDS)-272,147,1993)
INSTITUTE  (4RUSFEI)
REL-REF    (O,41155001,S.P.Simakov+,J,YK,,(3-4),74,1992) =
           (O,41155001,S.P.Simakov+,R,INDC(CCP)-358,74,1992)
            Data for Y and other isotopes - Co,Nb,In,TA,Bi.
FACILITY   (VDGT,4RUSFEI) EGP-10M tandem accelerator.
                 Pulse duration is 1.5 nsec, frequency 1.5 MHz
INC-SOURCE (P-T) Proton-tritium, gaseous tritium target
SAMPLE     Metallic yttrium of 4.4 cm height, 3.0 cm inner
           diameter, 4.5 cm outer diameter.
METHOD     (TOF) Flight base is 200 cm (scattered neutron
           registration), 401 cm (flux monitoring).
DETECTOR   (SCIN)
           (IOCH) For detector efficiency determination
MONITOR    (1-H-1(N,EL)1-H-1,,SIG)
MONIT-REF  (,A.Horsley,J,ND/A,2,243,1966)
STATUS     (APRVD) Simakov, 1983-06-25.
CORRECTION  Corrections were made on the neutron attenuation and
            on the multiple scattering in the sample
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S,2.,9.) Statistic-of-counts error
           (ERR-3,3.,7.) Detector energy-dependence uncertainty
                         error
           (ERR-5) Neutron flux determination error
           (ERR-6,5.,20.) For large energies and small angles -
                   elastic-scattering subtractions error
           (ERR-T) Total error.
HISTORY    (19830630C) Compiled at the centre
           (20060801U) Correction according to Memo CP-E/089.
            Dates were corrected for 4-digit year.  M.M.
           (20200311A) Corrections according to the comments of
           the author S.Simakov.
            Rep. ZFK-491 is not available for checking.
           Subents 003-007 were merged into Subent 003 according
           to a comment of N.Otsuka (NDS,IAEA)
           (20260216A) ANG-RSL was moved to Subent 003.
            STATUS was corrected for new rules.
ENDBIB              45
COMMON               1          3
ERR-5
PER-CENT
 4.0
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           52
SUBENT        40627002   20260216   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                  5         13
REACTION   (39-Y-89(N,X)0-NN-1,EM,SIG)
ANALYSIS   (INTED,INTAD)
           Exp. spectra were extrapolated in region below exp.
           threshold 0.6 MeV using Maxwellian distributions with
           parameter T determined in scattered neutrons energy
           range 0.6 - 2.0 MeV.
MISC-COL   (MISC) Parameter T, see ANALYSIS
STATUS     (TABLE,,S.Simakov+,R,ZFK-491,206,1982) Table 1.
           (DEP,40627003) DA/DE
           (SPSDD,41155011) Superseded according to a comment of
           the author S.Simakov ( almost the same data)
HISTORY    (20260216A) MISC data were added.
            (N,INL)39-Y-89,,SIG -> (N,X)0-NN-1,EM,,SIG
ENDBIB              13
NOCOMMON             0          0
DATA                 6          4
